Been MIA because I moved to the MIA 🌴

I decided 6 weeks ago to take the biggest leap I have taken in my adult life; moving to a completely new state. Ah! I’m so excited because I feel like I needed change and this is going to allow me to grow even more as a person and further my career and business. 

It’s been hard but I know this is for a greater purpose. I cannot wait to see what lays ahead and what doors will open in this new and exciting city. 

For those who have supported me all the way from when I was doing makeup at home - thank you for helping me grow, I wouldn’t be here if it weren’t for you and don’t worry, your favorite makeup artist and teacher is only a plane ride away ☁️

Cheers to new beginnings and remember it’s never too late to reinvent yourself 🍄🌴☁️👩🏻‍🎨

The importance of MINDSET ⤵️
How I get ready for a Bridal Makeup Appointment:

1. ☀️Rise and shine! Whether it’s with meditation, journaling, or simply taking a moment to center myself, starting the day off right is key.

2. 🧳Get organized, to slay the day. From packing my kit to checking directions and contact info, staying on top of things is crucial.

3. ☕️Keep the fire burning with breakfast and a cup of coffee. I wake up 2 hrs early to make sure I have time for breakfast and stop to grab a yummy cup of coffee so I'm ready to take on anything that comes my way.

⭐️By focusing on these three areas - starting strong, staying organized, and maintaining energy - I can arrive at my bride’s location feeling sharp, prepared, and ready to create a stunning makeup look that she’ll cherish forever.

#bridalmua #miamimakeupartist #makeupartist #muatips

Hi everyone.. You’ve joined me and my family in celebrating our beloved grandmother’s birthdays for years now.. Today, I’m cherishing those beautiful memories even more, as she’s recently left us to rest. 🕊️ 

Here’s a little about her story. Born in 1920, it all started when she fell for our grandfather. Their love story blossomed into a beautiful family—16 children, 49 grandchildren, 75 great-grandchildren, and 11 great-great-grandchildren (as per last year’s tally). Incredible, right?

But her legacy isn’t just about numbers. It’s in the love, resilience, and unity she instilled in us all. Simply put, we exist as we are because she lived as she was 🤍

We miss her dearly, but her spirit lives on in each of us. She’ll forever be our guiding light and the root of our family. 🌳

Here’s to her incredible journey as she continues to inspire us all and everyone who hears her story. 💕

#familylove #memories #grandmother #familymemories

Artist by day, guest by night! 👩🏻‍🎨💖
Pulled off this look in just 30 minutes. Here's how I did it:

🕒 Time-crunch hacks:
1️⃣ Skipped primer. Went right in with my trusty foundation and concealer, then set it.
2️⃣ No eyeshadow. Just used my finger to apply my favorite shimmer, added winged liner, and popped on a lash.
3️⃣ Focused on blush. It's all you can really see with my bob 💁🏻‍♀️
4️⃣ Lips? Did a quick lip liner and applied gloss on the car ride over.
5️⃣ Finished up with a setting spray and I was out!

What's the fastest you’ve gotten ready for a special event? 👀

So I just had an amazing realization 💅🏼✨

After moving, I unintentionally took a break from getting my nails done. But when I finally treated myself again, something clicked. 

Working on a client with my newly done nails, I felt an amazing shift. 

It wasn't just about feeling good with pretty nails. The nails somehow enhanced my work. 

Each makeup brush stroke felt more refined and controlled, my hands were steadier, every blend delicately flawless. My application became almost effortless. It's as if my nails whispered “You got this” to my hands. ✨

This got me thinking about how small changes, like getting your nails done, can impact our craft 🎨✨

Have you ever had a similar experience? 🌸 If a simple act of self-care has boosted your creativity or work, share your story or drop a 💅🏽. Let's explore the little things that secretly enhance our talents! 🌟💬

#nailart #makeupartist #creativeboost #nailtransformation #artistryunleashed #frenchnaildesign
